{"tid":264443,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Android創始人推出新手機　有幾把炮？ (05:35)","createTime":"2017-05-30T22:22:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T07:48:59.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"78ac7ff58e0cd2513831f47098e44b183dd7a877","tid":264443,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T22:22:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170531/img/20170531053532fi_p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20170531%2Fimg%2F20170531053532fi_p1.jpg&h=b79f3730&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n手機背後有一個磁性連接口，能夠接合不同的手機模組，包括360度相機。<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=o1PnGbzvBgrRCns9BvjyqZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=1755ff9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】由智能手機作業系統Android創始人Andy Rubin帶領的科技公司Essential周二披露了首款推出的新手機，名為PH-1。這款手機引入了一些有趣的功能，顯然要與兩大龍頭Apple及Samsung一較高下。<br />\n<br />\n從本文附圖可見，該手機的邊框幼細，令手機螢幕更大。而更值得留意的是，手機背後有一個磁性連接口，能夠接合不同的手機模組，其中包括訂購手機時附送的360度相機。<br />\n<br />\n價格方面，預訂價格為749美元(約6,441港元)，附送360度相機及128GB內置容量；淨機預訂價格則為699美元(約5,452港元)。不過，目前只接受美國預訂，尚未披露國際預訂安排。<br />\n<br />\n硬件配置方面，手機內置容量為128GB，並配備4GB記憶體及高通Snapdragon 835處理器。螢幕為5.7吋，比iPhone 7 Plus的5.5吋大一點；後置鏡頭1,300萬像素，前置鏡頭則為800萬像素，均支援4K影片拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n手機外殼材料為鈦(titanium)和陶瓷，提供4款顏色：亮黑、啞灰、純白和青銅綠色。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170531/20170531053532fi.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20170531%2F20170531053532fi.html&d=o1PnGbzvBgrRCns9BvjyqZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=0ee6fb3d\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170531/20170531053532fi.html</a>"},{"pid":"8178e95ec1f43c8e643e4b8385f7e986e377c81c","tid":264443,"uid":5399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T00:51:57.000Z","msg":"System呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都係android<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d328c1eb3c7fdd45c75aa5fb6c311e23e34f0cd","tid":264443,"uid":8042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T00:56:46.000Z","msg":"LG算唔算證實咗模組化係會仆直<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bec0815ff34191f219aeb5a2df543feb1fcc7a1f","tid":264443,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T00:58:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>LG算唔算證實咗模組化係會仆直<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMoto Z?"},{"pid":"7db62c81591d68bd85aa3aa4e2bae998e1458a20","tid":264443,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T00:59:56.000Z","msg":"冇3.5mm jack<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2cd21e1f81226444c7dfdfe6bbda88bb99ee0c2","tid":264443,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T01:19:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>LG算唔算證實咗模組化係會仆直<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nLG用開關扣 難開難拆<br />\n用強磁石扣 合理啲"},{"pid":"c41502c5104aa203d560de20034495dc68141619","tid":264443,"uid":36651,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T02:17:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/ph_1_color_white_moon_copy.1496137703.png-694x463.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2Fph_1_color_white_moon_copy.1496137703.png-694x463.jpeg&h=c53c9847&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個樣都幾似小米mix<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7278176b49e85b450e7380c08062a69b0db62c","tid":264443,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T02:20:01.000Z","msg":"狗屎垃圾都出到手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2831892cd3c741c2e79ccf8b9db54d05e26dd183","tid":264443,"uid":21427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,